## Hi, I'm Kurtis

I'm a Mechanical Engineering student at [U.Va.](www.seas.virginia.edu)

I intern developing software for the [Center for Open Science.](www.cos.io)

You can see what I build for work (and for play) on [Github.](www.github.com/kmjungersen)

I also drive busses for U.Va.'s bus service, [The University Transit Service.](www.virginia.edu/parking/uts/)

Feel free to check out my profile on [LinkedIn.](www.linkedin.com/in/kmjungersen)

If you want to get in touch, [shoot me an email!](mailto:Kurtis@kmjungersen.com)
